comments: During the contest, Queen (ORL) is bringing his arm into a vertical position and any contact with Monk's (SAC) arm on his driving shot attempt is deemed marginal.
Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm immediately slides off Sabonis' (SAC) shoulder and marginal contact occurs as both players come together in pursuit of the rebound.
Banchero (ORL) initiates contact with Sabonis' (SAC) head during the layup attempt.
Monk (SAC) deflects the pass by Queen (ORL) out of bounds and is the last player to touch the ball. Possession correctly remains with the Magic.
Barnes (SAC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Banchero (ORL) is still in possession of the ball when the 24 second shot clock expires.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his hands toward Queen (ORL) and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis releases away.
Okeke (ORL) legally contests Murray's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) and Barnes (SAC) mutually engage in marginal arm to arm contact off-ball.
Sabonis (SAC) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) establishes himself in Suggs' (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact. The initial contact during the screen occurs to Suggs' side.
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Queen's (ORL) path and absorbs the marginal contact as they come together during the pick.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Monk's (SAC) shot attempt at the basket.

Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL). Although the foul occurs after Banchero's gather, the play would not finish inside the LDB and the illegal contact occurred prior to the start of the upward shooting motion. A non-shooting foul is correctly assessed.
Suggs (ORL) slides his pivot foot to create space.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Suggs' (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and incidental foot to foot contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
During the rebound, Sabonis (SAC) briefly rests his hand on Banchero's (ORL) shoulder and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis deflects the loose ball away.
Queen (ORL) moves alongside Monk's (SAC) path and Monk slightly extends his left arm to initiate the marginal contact before Monk loses control of his dribble during the transition play.
After Suggs (ORL) secures the loose ball, Monk (SAC) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Suggs' arm when Suggs starts his dribble.
Monk (SAC) initiates contact to Suggs' (ORL) front that affects his SQBR as he brings the ball up the court.
Sabonis (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Banchero (ORL).
Banchero's (ORL) momentum legally takes him into the backcourt to retrieve the loose ball after it is cleanly dislodged by Sabonis (SAC).
Monk (SAC) brings his hands toward Queen's (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Queen's drive.
Bitadze (ORL) is moving alongside Monk's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Banchero (ORL) briefly grasps and immediately releases Barnes' (SAC) arm as marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Bitadze (ORL) legally contests and cleanly blocks Barnes' (SAC) driving shot attempt.
The shot attempt does not touch the rim and the 24 second shot clock expires while the Kings are still in possession of the ball.
Lyles (SAC) briefly engages and quickly disengages with Okeke (ORL) as marginal contact occurs when they move toward the perimeter.
Lyles (SAC) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Queen (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball and temporarily dislodges it away from Monk (SAC) after he receives the pass.
Bitadze (ORL) jumps alongside Monk's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his right arm down and initiates contact with Banchero's (ORL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Queen (ORL) and Monk (SAC) meet at the same spot and briefly engage in marginal contact off-ball.

After the dribble handoff, Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Queen's (ORL) path before the contact. However, Sabonis after assuming a legal position, he moves toward Queen by turning his body, and a foul was warranted.

Bitadze (ORL) contests the dunk attempt and marginal follow-through contact occurs as he grazes Sabonis' (SAC) head.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
After releasing the shot, Banchero's (ORL) left hand comes down onto Lyles' (SAC) body and marginal contact occurs after Lyles' legal contest.
Suggs (ORL) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
After losing control of the ball, Banchero (ORL) attempts to stop his forward momentum and marginal contact occurs as he comes together with Murray (SAC), who is established in his path.

Banchero (ORL) loses control of the ball on his gather without any contact occurring to him by a defender and it sails out of bounds. Banchero is last to touch the ball and possession should have been awarded to the Kings.
Murray (SAC) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Banchero's (ORL) layup attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) initially establishes himself in Black's (ORL) path, but then extends into his path as he attempts to avoid the screen.
Banchero (ORL) legally contests Monk's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Queen (ORL) and Suggs (ORL) legally contest Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact as he retracts his left arm from Suggs' (ORL) path. Any contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Queen (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the incidental contact as he defends Fox (SAC) during the drive.
Fox (SAC) contests Suggs' (ORL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Suggs (ORL) avoids contact with Sabonis' (SAC) arm during the steal attempt.
Suggs (ORL) legally contests and cleanly blocks Fox's (SAC) shot attempt.
Bitadze (ORL) jumps vertically and absorbs the incidental contact from Murray (SAC) as he legally contests the layup attempt.
Suggs (ORL) commits a take foul on Sabonis (SAC).
Okeke (ORL) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Fox (SAC) moves alongside Suggs' (ORL) path and marginal contact occurs as they briefly come together on the perimeter.
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (SAC) and Houstan (ORL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
